member.remarks:
Sample request:

    PUT /cities/{cityId}
    {
       "name": "Budapest",
       "country": "Hungary",
       "postOffice": "1117"
    }


Sample request:

    PUT /hotels/{hotelId}
    {
       "name": "Hotel Budapest",
       "owner": "Hungarian Hotels Ltd.",
       "street": "King lu, 19 st."
       "latitude": "15.9",
       "longitude": "20.5",
       "cityId": "{cityId}"
    }


Sample request:

    POST /login
    {
       "email": "sample@user.com",
       "password": "sample_password"
    }

This endpoint allows users to submit a review for a particular hotel identified by the provided .
